Package: pfamscanr
Type: Package
Title: An R client for EMBL-EBI's PfamScan API
Version: 0.1-9999
Authors@R: c(person("George", "Vega Yon", role=c("aut","cre"),
         email="g.vegayon@gmail.com", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3171-0844")),
         person("National Cancer Institute (NCI)", role = "fnd",
         comment = "Grant Number 5P01CA196569-02"))
Description: The EMBL-EBI's "PfamScan" API <doi:10.1093/nar/gkz268> is used to
  search a FASTA sequence against a library of Pfam HMM. This R client manages
  the connection with the API, in particular, posting the query, checking the
  status, and collecting the results.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
  httr,
  jsonlite,
  utils
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
